      • setup

        public void setup(Consumer<String> failedLayoutCallback)
        Sets up the LayoutManager by loading all layouts from the layouts/ folder.

        This method should not be called manually. AdvancedGUI makes sure that the Manager is always setup.
        Parameters:
        failedLayoutCallback - will be called with the file name of json files that could not be parsed as a layout
